[exhales]

33:45.588 --> 33:47.155
- [gasps]
Hailey, oh, my God.

33:47.199 --> 33:49.331
I am so sorry.

33:49.375 --> 33:50.767
- Don't touch me!
- I don't know what happened.

33:50.811 --> 33:52.073
I lost track of the days.

33:52.117 --> 33:53.727
- You forgot
my birthday, Mom.

33:53.770 --> 33:55.207
- How is that possible?

33:55.250 --> 33:56.643
