33:56.686 --> 33:57.948
- I don't know.

33:59.124 --> 34:01.865
- There's something
happening to me.

34:01.909 --> 34:04.085
Ever since...

34:04.129 --> 34:05.565
Something I can't remember.

34:05.608 --> 34:10.091
