34:24.279 --> 34:25.759
and you wanted to know
who your dad was.

34:25.802 --> 34:27.021
You never talked about it,

34:27.065 --> 34:28.153
but I know you thought about it
all the time.

34:28.196 --> 34:29.371
Maybe it's something
like that.

34:29.415 --> 34:30.938
Or maybe it's nothing
like that.

34:30.981 --> 34:34.376
You probably think
I'm losing my mind.

34:34.420 --> 34:37.945
- It's all right.
I got a cake at school.

34:37.988 --> 34:39.729
- A cake, that's good.
That's good.

34:39.773 --> 34:41.949
