a nice birthday.

34:44.952 --> 34:46.127
I got to go.

34:46.171 --> 34:48.651
- Mom, no.
- I know what I have to do now.

34:49.826 --> 34:52.002
- Mom, don't go.
Please stay.

34:54.788 --> 34:57.051
- Happy birthday, baby.

35:00.185 --> 35:02.839
- Mom.

35:03.231 --> 35:04.276
[door slams]

35:05.799 --> 35:08.628
[suspenseful music]

35:08.671 --> 35:15.722
♪

35:17.202 --> 35:20.683
